class Solution:
    def groupAnagrams(self, s: str) -> List[List[str]]:
        ans = []
        
        anagram_dict = {}
        
        for i in range(len(s)):
            if s[i] not in anagram_dict:
                anagram_dict[s[i]] = [s[i]]
            else:
                anagram_dict[s[i]].append(s[i])
                
        for key, value in sorted(anagram_dict.items()):
            ans.append(value)
            
        return ans
